*Today on the day of love, the neighbor has again shown love.*
*Snake's nature to spew poison has spewed poison again*.

When 44 lions fell on the earth, the light of mother earth went out.
*Mehndi bangle bindi mahavar forehead's vermilion gone.*

* Papa will give toys, we are sitting in this love *.
Children will play Holi together, waiting.

* Children don't know that India has suffered the pain of mother *.
*Papa played Holi of blood a month back.*

Whose blood became water, he remained unconscious at home.
All those who lick the feet of politics remained silent.

* My mouth is full of abuses, I will not be able to take a decision.
* I am bound in rituals, I will not be able to abuse.

This scene, this weather all seems like a waste.
Even my own face looks like a criminal to me.

* As many soldiers died here, my fault is also there *.
I also have one vote in the Delhi where you are sitting.

* It is very important to burst the same womb when terror emerges.
It is very important to eradicate Islamic terrorism.

* Jackals were sent as lions are lying in Delhi *.
All three monkeys are lying sick of Gandhi in Delhi.

Whatever the army has to do, let it go Modi ji.
* Then Modi ji let the lions go inside the border.

You fight with the enemy, we will bear everything inside.
Will eat food at one time or will remain hungry.

Show the power that the lions have at the border.
Make everything expensive but increase the defense budget.

O soldier, I tell you to pick up the gun now.
* Or come home from the border and pick up your box *.

Listen to the lions of CRPF, listen to the jawans of all the forces.
*Khaki people just listen and the soldiers listen to the pride of the country*.

*Break all the actions of the enemy in your company.*
*Keep 47 and AK-56 loaded for 24 hours.*

*Don't tolerate any bullet, just do this much.*
*You fill the entire magazine in the enemy's chest.*

*You don't take any cowardly message, soldier.*
*Soldiers don't obey orders to retreat.*

You pick up the gun and climb on the chest of terrorism.
You go ahead even after crossing the line of LOC.

*Give the answer to all the traitors in their own colors.*
